dct_title_s: Raccoon Creek, New Jersey from Swedesboro to Springer's Wharf
dct_description_sm: Map 1: Raccoon Creek from Molonox Shoal to Swedesboro.

Map shows Raccoon Creek with soundings, the 7 foot curve and 4 foot curve, the mean low water line, proposed improvements and jetty. There is a diagram of the New Highway Draw Bridge, a detail of survey near the new highway draw bridge, and a locality sketch.
Map 2: Raccoon Creek from Springer's Bar to Shorn's Wharf.
Map shows Raccoon Creek with soundings and some wharfs along the creek.
Map 3: Raccoon Creek from Delaware River to Potato Hills Shoal.
Map shows soundings of Delaware River and Raccoon Creek. Also shows Raccoon Island.
dcat_keyword_sm: River and Harbor Act of March 4, 1913
